{"tid":682663,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"小米 8 都有 Animoji！由外抄到內？！","createTime":"2018-05-29T05:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T08:01:00.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"e872eb54c1990d8a1277b0e711d8c0438db80b69","tid":682663,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:00:32.000Z","msg":"今次小米 8 由外形到硬件配置甚至售價全部「呼之欲出」，幾乎可以不用看發布會直播，加上今早釋出的短片，幾可肯定小米 8 將會是一部「超高仿」iPhone X<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，皆因短片是一系列動態動物表情符號，意味小米 8 會內建跟 iPhone X TrueDepth 鏡頭相似的相機模組，能模擬用戶面部表情製作出動態表情，與蘋果 Animoji 的相似度高達 99%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有網民看過後更留言小米 8 這個新功能是否叫 minimoji<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2080000/2082239/28052018suet_04_600.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2080000%2F2082239%2F28052018suet_04_600.gif&h=1aaf49f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2082239/小米+8+都有+Animoji！由外抄到內？！\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2082239%2F%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%2B8%2B%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%2BAnimoji%EF%BC%81%E7%94%B1%E5%A4%96%E6%8A%84%E5%88%B0%E5%85%A7%EF%BC%9F%EF%BC%81&d=MFJqdupFcKWnelv73%2FLeohOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=3f34ddf2\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2082239/小米+8+都有+Animoji！由外抄到內？！</a></div>"},{"pid":"dc73f1e9aafcc639b4b134a757ab50bc1484a914","tid":682663,"uid":1886,"like":9,"dislike":10,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T05:02:21.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180515/large/1526369384_b5a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt